<p>John and Dave talk and troubleshoot video issues, motherboard issues, and connecting to a headless Mac. Then it&rsquo;s time for a discussion about tracking email recipients, and Dave even tells his crazy story about the guy who had gremlins in his computer &mdash; and got &lsquo;em out! Don&rsquo;t miss it.</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
